### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@fundId = fund-uuid-here
@accountId = account-uuid-here
@campaignId = pledge-campaign-uuid-here

### Create a new fund
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/funds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "General Fund",
  "description": "Main church operations fund",
  "targetAmount": 1000000.0,
  "isRestricted": false
}

### List funds
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/funds

### Create pledge campaign (Gracely “Create campaign”)
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/pledge-campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Building 2026",
  "fundId": "{{fundId}}",
  "startDate": "2026-04-11",
  "endDate": "2027-04-11"
}

### Pledge campaigns dashboard (summary + table rows; same as Gracely pledge-accounts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/pledge-campaigns?filter=all&search=

### Alias path (matches Gracely URL segment)
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/pledge-accounts?filter=in_progress

### Completed campaigns tab
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/pledge-campaigns?filter=completed

### List pledges in a campaign
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/pledge-campaigns/{{campaignId}}/pledges

### Create member pledge (optional pledgeCampaignId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/pledges
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-uuid-here",
  "fundId": "{{fundId}}",
  "pledgeCampaignId": "{{campaignId}}",
  "targetAmount": 1200,
  "startDate": "2026-04-11",
  "endDate": "2027-04-11"
}

### Create financial account (Gracely “Create Account” modal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Operating Checking",
  "code": "878",
  "type": "asset",
  "description": "Main operating bank",
  "fundId": "{{fundId}}",
  "openingBalance": 0,
  "openingDate": "2026-04-11"
}

### Accounting overview (KPIs + table; Gracely /accounting)
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/accounting?filter=all&search=

### Asset tab
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/accounting?filter=asset

### List all ledger accounts (includes non–chart-of-accounts types)
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/accounts

### Record a transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500.0,
  "description": "Sunday Offering Deposit",
  "type": "credit",
  "fundId": "{{fundId}}"
}

### List transactions for an account
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/finance/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions
